{"tid":1355453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】何君堯肯定會扶搖直上","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:15:06.000Z","uid":85252,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1af0813f8bd1074c529059e8c498317d49f3f811","tid":1355453,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"勝和呢次搞何君堯家墳，後果除咗為何君堯增添慘情外，更為佢可以向中共加碼拎維穩費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n激進派的意義從來都係以激進行為令輿論失焦，白衫恐襲的邪惡顯然係比送中條例來得直接，搞埋何君堯家墳更加係令到四大訴求無咗影<br />\n<br />\n好似何君堯呢啲無良心嘅鼠輩，唔通佢會為何新榮個墳肉痛咩﹖佢係原居民定養仔都未知呀﹗但佢就可以依此來乞班深藍票，轉個頭又可以收割埋維穩費。對於呢條契弟，今日無嘢輸之餘，直頭係贏到開巷<br />\n<br />\n所以大家為勝和喝采完，爽完又想真正收對家皮，就又係時候重申四大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 撤回《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n2. 收回6‧12「暴動」定性<br />\n3. 撤銷有關反送中一事的所有控罪<br />\n4. 設立獨立委員會追究警隊濫權</span></span>"},{"pid":"3c755072ec6abbdb7111f3e96e3478b66943df51","tid":1355453,"uid":235465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大</span></span>"},{"pid":"dee120fc57201e2c1024004784054bc9c882966a","tid":1355453,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c755072ec6abbdb7111f3e96e3478b66943df51","tid":1355453,"uid":235465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 立即實行雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n巴打啱"}]}